---
import '../styles/tailwind.css'
---

<section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 bg-[#f2f0f6]" id="advantages">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left Column with Heading and Image -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Challenges solved by 
            <span class="text-blue-500 block md:inline">MindMate.ai</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="relative mt-8">
            <!-- AI Character Image -->
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <img 
                src="/image.png" 
                alt="AI Sales Assistant" 
                class="w-64 h-auto"
              />
            </div>
            
            <!-- Blue Triangle Background -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 h-64 bg-blue-500 opacity-30 rounded-full filter blur-xl z-0"></div>
            
            <!-- Chat Button -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-2 flex items-center">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-200 mr-2 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=40&width=40" alt="Support Agent" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-blue-500 text-white p-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10c0 3.866-3.582 7-8 7a8.841 8.841 0 01-4.083-.98L2 17l1.338-3.123C2.493 12.767 2 11.434 2 10c0-3.866 3.582-7 8-7s8 3.134 8 7zM7 9H5v2h2V9zm8 0h-2v2h2V9zM9 9h2v2H9V9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Right Column with Challenges List -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">Lack of 24/7 availability
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">Expensive mental health tools
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">High dropout rates in therapy, with clients losing motivation before seeing lasting improvements.
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">Poor process automation</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">Inconsistent follow-ups with clients, leading to missed opportunities for effective intervention.
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">Therapists struggle to maintain consistent client engagement due to limited time and resources.
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">Long hours and high turnover rates in therapy practices, leading to burnout and decreased quality of care.
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-gray-800">High operational costs for mental health professionals, making quality therapy inaccessible to many.
            </span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  